snippet.title: Sonic Heroes Puzzle
snippet.description:
A puzzle game based on Sonic Heroes.

Game link: http://web.archive.org/web/20041211053510/http://www.sega.com/gamesite/sonicheroes/minigame/flash/ 

(If the website doesn't work, it probably has some problems.)

Note: Game requires Adobe Flash Player.
